# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Released]
## [0.2.5] - 10-04-2022
### Fixed
- Resolve problem show disk space

## [0.2.4] - 10-04-2022
### Fixed
- Resolve problem get urls for episodes during download in parallel
- UpdateService also update the renaming of a file

### Add
- Show information space disk
- Show information health of services
- Add slide bar for see informations

## [0.2.3] - 08-04-2022
### Add
- Webhook Discord for log

### Fixed
- Module HtmlAnimeSaturn now work in parallel for download urls of episodes
- Module Download now work in parallel for second method (use with buffers) of episodes
- Fixed overflow memory when calculate hash of one episode over 1GB size

## [0.2.2] - 06-04-2022
### Add
- Setup default environment global

### Fixed
- Change structure for logger

## [0.2.1] - 05-04-2022
### Add
- Notify service that send messages to Discord with Webhook

### Fixed
- Add environment logger for reduced lines of log

## [0.2.0] - 01-04-2022
### Add
- Tracking files and movements (modified class models and added new table)
- Check Hash256
- Browser support now Mobile
- Add all description of an anime into card, if anime not already downloaded show a link for redirect original page with information

### Fixed
- Improve call API
- Improve conversion class model to class dto or reverse
- If Anime already downloaded not show button for download episodes

### Changed
- Split two part of UpdateService, UpdateService check integry files on local and UpgradeService check new or missing episodes into db
- Buttons Search
- Size pagination
- replace 'previous' and 'next' with arrows in pagination
- Show status of downloads after press a button


## [0.1.2] - 29-03-2022
### Add
- Add button re-download anime if download are stop

### Fixed
- when download is filed, bar progress is red with write 'filed' instead of percentual with value 100%
- when download is completed, bar progress is green with write 'completed' instead of percentual
- Resolve problem open file

### Changed
- DownloadService start timeout 0 to max limit defined and print log if error download with attempts remains, if download is success reset timeout

## [0.1.1] - 29-03-2022
### Added
- new button into bar search for get all anime

### Changed
- color buttons into bar search


## [0.1.0] - 27-03-2022
### Version Stable